            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pulled chicken & gravy </strong>over the <strong>cheesy sweet potato fries</strong>, with the <strong>buttered greens</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
